{"tid":2147281,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"慈愛苑居民：幫孩子撩喉夾硬嚟","createTime":"2020-08-09T06:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T10:07:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dae0c43bed3bef1ab5054f6f36a357808660243e","tid":2147281,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:43:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200809/BBM72CVANLY6C2J3Z4UNYE6V2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200809%2FBBM72CVANLY6C2J3Z4UNYE6V2Y%2F&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminEx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=95149a71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200809%2FBBM72CVANLY6C2J3Z4UNYE6V2Y%2F&h=19b5a3c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200809/BBM72CVANLY6C2J3Z4UNYE6V2Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n慈愛苑居民：幫孩子撩喉夾硬嚟<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】率先以「咽拭子採樣」方式檢測武漢肺炎的慈雲山慈愛苑居民，昨晨陸續。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：化驗師與外判關係複雜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OrH3rPv9wcq08CumO7Bu-Bglsa4=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JXRUAYSFJT2JQ5ZCNCCX7X2BAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOrH3rPv9wcq08CumO7Bu-Bglsa4%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJXRUAYSFJT2JQ5ZCNCCX7X2BAU.jpg&h=fc3734d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工作人員在慈愛苑設咽拭子樣本收集站，用夾子收取居民的樣本樽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「想嘔出嚟 好唔舒服」<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。，雖然有專家質疑咽拭子採樣會引致咳嗽，恐有播毒風險，政府前日仍按計劃首次向慈愛苑居民派發咽拭子採樣套裝，昨回收樣本樽。<br />\n<br />\n昨晨8時許，身穿全套保護衣工作人員在大。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不少居民表示咽拭子採樣方法令人感到不適及取樣較困難，認為若有專業醫護人員為居民取樣本會較好，「自己撩（取樣）唔知夠唔夠佢化驗」。居民黃先生指取樣期間曾感到不適，「試過有一下想嘔出嚟，好唔舒服，觸碰到敏感點」。陳先生則稱為6歲孩子取樣時特別困難，要「夾硬嚟」才能完成取樣，「佢好抗拒，大人做（採樣）都會有少少不適，可能由醫護人員做（採樣）會好啲。」"},{"pid":"2aeb4048f8ae43ebffd544163b0cf363dffe5396","tid":2147281,"uid":181549,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:46:08.000Z","msg":"一撩啲病毒飛撚哂出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35c7f159d16c4b79e3c58eeca5aba042be0c1bf","tid":2147281,"uid":201604,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:47:38.000Z","msg":"我喉嚨仲係處 唔想畀武漢肺炎破左"},{"pid":"6c7eeacee08b00699b6de3fc881942d3fb7e5da3","tid":2147281,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:47:40.000Z","msg":"的確係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19710bad55a37c528ab3f1f04124933551f8fe8e","tid":2147281,"uid":10093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:50:57.000Z","msg":"醫護採集其實都係會令人咁辛苦<br />\n一係留深喉唾液lor<br />\n反正當局話兩者相等"},{"pid":"2b420da82aaa679208a9e055bf0d9b288a12eebb","tid":2147281,"uid":188411,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:56:38.000Z","msg":"遲吓啲器官都係咁，集慣下先囉，反正香港人有份爭取全民檢測"},{"pid":"e160f2e2659b3f548622025f819691c8f256c7b6","tid":2147281,"uid":55851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:04:50.000Z","msg":"係一定會嘔，因為要掂到喉嚨，仲隊得入過啲人扣喉"},{"pid":"be7a072305bece24fc393802319ec2544af5ac8f","tid":2147281,"uid":59242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:05:46.000Z","msg":"醫護做都係會唔舒服 <br />\n聽電台訪問中招病人，撩到標眼水想嘔都要忍"},{"pid":"2d4634efc1e79929ddaa28deed18b9a2a3aab1ec","tid":2147281,"uid":3860,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2b420da82aaa679208a9e055bf0d9b288a12eebb","tid":2147281,"uid":188411,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:56:38.000Z","msg":"遲吓啲器官都係咁，集慣下先囉，反正香港人有份爭取全民檢測"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:06:07.000Z","msg":"又老屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左藍屍邊個要全民檢測<br />\n<br />\n又係傻鳩係到眾人皆醉你獨醒<br />\n正柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hk